</header>
<br/>
				<p>
					VIOUSLY collects and uses the Data to (i) operate the Site and the Platform, (ii) to deliver the Services selected upon Your subscription to the Platform (notably any revenue sharing if applicable) and, (iii), from time to time, to inform and/or propose to You other products or services available on the Platform.<br/><br/>Furthermore, VIOUSLY uses the Data to provide general statistics regarding the use of the Site and the Platform such as to determine what VIOUSLY services are the most popular.<br/><br/>VIOUSLY may also contact You via surveys to conduct research about Your opinion of current services or of potential new services that may be offered on the Platform.
				</p>
			</div>
			</article>
			<article class="card scrollspy" id="privacy-data-transfert">
