</header>
<br/>
				<p>
					You are entitled to access, correct and/or ask for the deletion of Your Data.<br/><br/>You can do so via Your personal Settings and account information and/or by sending a letter to the following address: VIOUSLY, 278 chaussée Fernand Forest, 59200 Tourcoing France. <br/><br/>You can also opt-out of receiving announcements of certain information by following the unsubscribe instructions provided in the promotional e-mail You receive, by sending us an email to : <a href="mailto:contact@viously.com">contact@viously.com</a>.
				</p>
